snippet.title: PROJECT MORPH Prototype Teaser
snippet.description:
Transform into the monsters you kill!

Collect enemy DNA to transform into various creatures, so called "MORPHS".
Become your enemy, literally and fight fire with fire! 

Prototype powered by Gamecity Hamburg
